file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: "1.0"
  title: Root vendor extensions
  description: Should be copied over without generating additional schemas
x-something:
  one:
    identifier: "1"
    url: https://one.com
  another:
    identifier: Not1
    url: https://another.com
x-something-groups:
  first:
    - color: green
      default:
        backend:
          $ref: "#/x-something/one"
      options:
        - backend:
            $ref: "#/x-something/another"
          criteria:
            - in: header
              name: x-value-id
              value:
                - 42
    - color: blue
      default:
        backend:
          $ref: "#/x-something/one"
      options:
        - backend:
            $ref: "#/x-something/another"
          criteria:
            - in: header
              name: x-value-id
              value:
                - 17
paths:
  /v1/check:
    get:
      operationId: one
      summary: Gets check
      description: Cf. summary.
      x-backends:
        $ref: "#/x-something-groups/first"
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Successful request.
        "400":
          description: Bad request.
servers:
  - url: https://example.com/an/api
